FT  26 JUL 94 / UK Company News: Sherwood Computer
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Sherwood Computer Services, has sold Sherwood Consort Data, its subsidiary
providing software and services to the stockbroking market, to its
management for a maximum of Pounds 450,000.
