1,000. It had a net deficit on reserves of Pounds 33,000.
Sherwood Computer received Pounds 250,000 on completion and will receive a
further consideration up to a maximum Pounds 200,000 payable as a royalty on
licence sales. Proceeds will reduce the company's overdraft.
